Initial commit: aiforpet SDK Flutter demo

- StartActivityScreen invokes the SDK via MethodChannel
  (com.aiforpet.sdk/channel) for DOG and CAT diagnostic parts.
- Result payloads pretty-printed as indented JSON, with raw-text
  fallback on FormatException.
- Pet/part catalog refactored to a data-driven PetSection model;
  background and per-pet card colors extracted as constants.
- widget_test mocks the platform channel and exercises rendering,
  the option-toggle path, and the launchSdk -> result-overlay flow
  (3/3 passing, flutter analyze clean).
- README documents the channel contract and run/verify commands.
- .gitignore excludes .bkit/ and .omc/ tooling state.

